dudes is my real father!

00:04:56.338 --> 00:05:00.050 position:50% align:center
The question is, which one?

00:05:00.133 --> 00:05:01.968 position:50% align:center
Wow, for real?

00:05:02.052 --> 00:05:03.470 position:50% align:center
Check it, I feel
like this guy and I

00:05:03.553 --> 00:05:06.181 position:50% align:center
might have
the same eyebrows.

00:05:06.264 --> 00:05:09.267 position:50% align:center
That said, I have no way
of actually knowing.

00:05:09.351 --> 00:05:10.602 position:50% align:center
And if I were being honest,

00:05:10.685 --> 00:05:13.021 position:50% align:center
it might not be
any of these men.

00:05:13.104 --> 00:05:15.023 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
What do you mean?

00:05:15.106 --> 00:05:17.317 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
This woman promised.

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:18.693 position:50% align:center
When I got into middle school,

00:05:18.777 --> 00:05:20.612 position:50% align:center
I could meet my real dad.

00:05:20.695 --> 00:05:24.074 position:50% align:center
But then, she bailed on me.

00:05:25.241 --> 00:05:26.826 position:50% align:center
