what's with the long face?

00:05:43.259 --> 00:05:44.511 position:50% align:center
Don't worry.

00:05:44.594 --> 00:05:46.554 position:50% align:center
I gave birth to you,
so if nothing else,

00:05:46.638 --> 00:05:49.015 position:50% align:center
