pissed me off the most.

00:05:57.857 --> 00:06:00.652 position:50% align:center
That sucks.

00:06:00.735 --> 00:06:02.195 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I know!

00:06:02.278 --> 00:06:04.489 position:50% align:center
I'd probably get
along great with my dad.

00:06:04.572 --> 00:06:08.243 position:50% align:center
I bet you that's the real reason
why she won't let me meet him.

00:06:08.326 --> 00:06:09.703 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
You think?

00:06:09.786 --> 00:06:12.831 position:50% align:center
She'll do anything to
stop me from being happy.

00:06:12.914 --> 00:06:14.499 position:50% align:center
