persecution complex

00:06:14.582 --> 00:06:16.793 position:50% align:center
and thinks she some
kinda tragic heroine.

00:06:16.876 --> 00:06:18.378 position:50% align:center
That's enough.

00:06:19.587 --> 00:06:22.966 position:50% align:center
