to you insult your mother.

00:06:23.049 --> 00:06:23.925 position:50% align:center
What the heck?

00:06:24.009 --> 00:06:25.927 position:50% align:center
I thought you were on my side.

00:06:26.011 --> 00:06:29.014 position:50% align:center
I am, it's why I said something.

00:06:39.941 --> 00:06:41.192 position:50% align:center
Look, it's not like I enjoy

00:06:41.276 --> 00:06:43.361 position:50% align:center
