mom or whatever.

00:06:43.445 --> 00:06:44.738 position:50% align:center
But you know,

00:06:44.821 --> 00:06:47.240 position:50% align:center
she's not out winning
any mom of the year awards.

00:06:47.323 --> 00:06:49.784 position:50% align:center
Like, she throws a fit
when things don't go her way,

00:06:49.868 --> 00:06:52.871 position:50% align:center
and all she does is tell me
a bunch of half-assed lies.

00:06:52.954 --> 00:06:56.791 position:50% align:center
She's never once told me
that she's sorry for anything!

00:06:56.875 --> 00:07:00.378 position:50% align:center
The only thing she cares
about is her stupid pride.

00:07:00.462 --> 00:07:03.048 position:50% align:center
Always ranting about how she
"should have been happier."

00:07:03.131 --> 00:07:04.841 position:50% align:center
As if it it's not her own fault.

00:07:04.924 --> 00:07:07.010 position:50% align:center
I think that's why
she hates me so much.

00:07:07.093 --> 00:07:09.304 position:50% align:center
I honestly believe she feels
like her life would be easier

00:07:09.387 --> 00:07:11.931 position:50% align:center
if I were never in
the picture to begin with.

00:07:15.977 --> 00:07:19.647 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE] I'm sure
your mom has her reasons.

00:07:19.731 --> 00:07:23.526 position:50% align:center
From the sound of it,
you hate her, too.

00:07:23.610 --> 00:07:26.404 position:50% align:center
