called "codependence."

00:07:27.238 --> 00:07:30.492 position:50% align:center
If you don't make a clean break,
then nothing will change.

00:07:30.575 --> 00:07:31.618 position:50% align:center
I don't need a dumb lecture

00:07:31.701 --> 00:07:33.870 position:50% align:center
from some goody
two shoes like you!

00:07:33.953 --> 00:07:35.330 position:50% align:center
I'm outta here.

00:07:35.413 --> 00:07:37.332 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Rika!

00:07:37.415 --> 00:07:38.833 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Rika!

00:07:49.761 --> 00:07:51.137 position:50% align:center
