Disgusting.

00:08:03.441 --> 00:08:04.693 position:50% align:center
Hey, Ai.

00:08:04.776 --> 00:08:07.028 position:50% align:center
I figured you'd chase after me.

00:08:07.112 --> 00:08:08.613 position:50% align:center
Oh, yeah?

00:08:08.697 --> 00:08:11.074 position:50% align:center
