00:08:34.514 --> 00:08:35.265 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Ai.

00:08:35.348 --> 00:08:36.599 position:50% align:center
Yeah?

00:08:36.683 --> 00:08:38.727 position:50% align:center
I'm Serious Rika now.

00:08:38.810 --> 00:08:40.603 position:50% align:center
So, I'd like to be honest.

00:08:40.687 --> 00:08:41.730 position:50% align:center
