00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:44.441 position:50% align:center
All right.

00:08:44.524 --> 00:08:47.152 position:50% align:center
Do you wanna
tell me about earlier?

00:08:47.235 --> 00:08:48.737 position:50% align:center
