all the bad memories

00:08:48.820 --> 00:08:51.031 position:50% align:center
just sort of hit me at once.

00:08:51.114 --> 00:08:53.867 position:50% align:center
That must have been
really hard for you.

00:08:55.827 --> 00:08:57.454 position:50% align:center
