00:12:27.414 --> 00:12:32.043 position:50% align:center
[laughter]

00:12:32.127 --> 00:12:33.169 position:50% align:center
[CUSTOMER C]
She's at that age.

00:12:33.253 --> 00:12:34.587 position:50% align:center
[CHIAKI]
Always!

00:12:34.671 --> 00:12:36.506 position:50% align:center
[CUSTOMER D]
She has her mother's eyes.

00:12:36.589 --> 00:12:38.508 position:50% align:center
[CHIAKI]
I'll take that as a compliment.

00:12:38.591 --> 00:12:41.052 position:50% align:center
[CUSTOMER A] Will you carry
on this place together?

00:12:41.136 --> 00:12:42.721 position:50% align:center
[CHIAKI] Who knows?
Youth is wasted on the young!

00:12:42.804 --> 00:12:45.432 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Yeah. Drop dead.

00:12:55.608 --> 00:12:59.154 position:50% align:center
No... I can't...

00:13:10.749 --> 00:13:14.002 position:50% align:center
My little turtle, Mannen. <i>Redi.</i>

00:13:17.505 --> 00:13:20.675 position:50% align:center
<i>Redi.</i> Come back, okay?

00:13:20.759 --> 00:13:23.303 position:50% align:center
[SHINO] Your worries
are about to go away.

00:13:23.386 --> 00:13:26.222 position:50% align:center
Vanish! Pooof, all gone!

00:13:26.306 --> 00:13:28.433 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Ugh, who's the freak show?

00:13:28.516 --> 00:13:29.559 position:50% align:center
My teacher!

00:13:29.642 --> 00:13:31.144 position:50% align:center
The only one who
can tell you to connect

00:13:31.227 --> 00:13:32.687 position:50% align:center
with the cosmic truth!

00:13:32.771 --> 00:13:35.065 position:50% align:center
Yes, entrust everything to me.

00:13:35.148 --> 00:13:37.150 position:50% align:center
Do so, and you shall be saved!

00:13:37.233 --> 00:13:38.193 position:50% align:center
Saved!

00:13:38.276 --> 00:13:40.528 position:50% align:center
Sorry, creep,
I don't need saving!

00:13:47.535 --> 00:13:49.454 position:50% align:center
Take this!

00:13:50.705 --> 00:13:52.457 position:50% align:center
[SHINO screams]

00:13:56.336 --> 00:13:57.128 position:50% align:center
That's that.

00:13:57.212 --> 00:13:58.546 position:50% align:center
Stupid old wind bag.

00:13:58.630 --> 00:14:00.757 position:50% align:center
What have you done? Why
would you attack our teacher?

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:02.050 position:50% align:center
Teacher?

00:14:02.133 --> 00:14:04.678 position:50% align:center
Yes, of love, the universe,
and the spiritual!

00:14:04.761 --> 00:14:06.346 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:14:06.429 --> 00:14:07.847 position:50% align:center
[SHINO]
Mother was in poor health

00:14:07.931 --> 00:14:10.016 position:50% align:center
and Father was
struggling at work.

00:14:10.100 --> 00:14:12.811 position:50% align:center
We were cursed by karma
from our past lives!

00:14:12.894 --> 00:14:17.190 position:50% align:center
So that's why we got rid
of them, earthly attachments!

00:14:17.273 --> 00:14:19.275 position:50% align:center
We abandoned our house,
money, everything,

00:14:19.359 --> 00:14:22.737 position:50% align:center
so our whole family could
connect to the cosmos instead!

00:14:22.821 --> 00:14:23.988 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Are you stupid?

00:14:24.072 --> 00:14:26.116 position:50% align:center
You got swindled and
then killed yourselves.

00:14:29.911 --> 00:14:32.831 position:50% align:center
You say that,
yet you suffer, too.

00:14:33.707 --> 00:14:36.334 position:50% align:center
[CENTIPEDE] Deep down,
we're all the same inside.

00:14:36.418 --> 00:14:40.213 position:50% align:center
Everyone is fixated on worthless
appearances and hierarchies.

00:14:40.296 --> 00:14:42.257 position:50% align:center
Those who have grow arrogant

00:14:42.340 --> 00:14:44.759 position:50% align:center
and those who have
not grow envious.

00:14:44.843 --> 00:14:48.096 position:50% align:center
Talk about your new-age BS.

00:14:48.179 --> 00:14:50.765 position:50% align:center
Says the girl who cuts herself.

00:14:52.517 --> 00:14:56.021 position:50% align:center
So join us and vanish.

00:14:56.104 --> 00:14:58.106 position:50% align:center
It's much easier.

00:14:58.189 --> 00:15:00.150 position:50% align:center
You'll feel better.

00:15:01.568 --> 00:15:03.153 position:50% align:center
It can be easier?

00:15:03.236 --> 00:15:04.571 position:50% align:center
[SHINO]
Yes.

00:15:04.654 --> 00:15:07.490 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Acca, tell me how Rika's doing.

00:15:07.574 --> 00:15:10.493 position:50% align:center
[ACCA] You should focus
on your own battles.

00:15:10.577 --> 00:15:13.079 position:50% align:center
[AI]
She was crying, I'm worried.

00:15:13.163 --> 00:15:14.831 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
Rika might be in a fix.

00:15:14.914 --> 00:15:16.124 position:50% align:center
Ura-Acca.

00:15:16.207 --> 00:15:17.000 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Please!

00:15:17.083 --> 00:15:18.918 position:50% align:center
Tell me what's happening to her!

00:15:19.878 --> 00:15:23.089 position:50% align:center
Well, she's...
given up on fighting.

00:15:24.174 --> 00:15:27.635 position:50% align:center
[CENTIPEDE] Relax, my child,
everyone who is held in my arms

00:15:27.719 --> 00:15:30.680 position:50% align:center
are linked to the
mysteries of the cosmos.

00:15:30.764 --> 00:15:33.224 position:50% align:center
You're still too tense.

00:15:35.352 --> 00:15:37.479 position:50% align:center
Don't worry.

00:15:38.521 --> 00:15:39.773 position:50% align:center
[CENTIPEDE]
See?

00:15:39.856 --> 00:15:41.649 position:50% align:center
It doesn't hurt, does it?

00:15:41.733 --> 00:15:43.276 position:50% align:center
No.

00:15:43.360 --> 00:15:45.737 position:50% align:center
[CENTIPEDE]
There's nothing to be afraid of.

00:15:45.820 --> 00:15:48.490 position:50% align:center
Your tiny self can
become something greater,

00:15:48.573 --> 00:15:51.910 position:50% align:center
you can be part
of a vast energy.

00:15:51.993 --> 00:15:53.828 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
My tiny self.

00:15:53.912 --> 00:15:56.206 position:50% align:center
[SHINO] Yes, you'll become
one with the teacher.

00:15:56.289 --> 00:15:58.583 position:50% align:center
[CENTIPEDE]
There's no need to envy others.

00:15:58.667 --> 00:16:02.087 position:50% align:center
You don't need to
hate anyone ever again.

00:16:02.170 --> 00:16:03.838 position:50% align:center
You'll erase your bad karma

00:16:03.922 --> 00:16:06.383 position:50% align:center
and become one
with the universe.

00:16:06.466 --> 00:16:08.009 position:50% align:center
That sounds great.

00:16:08.093 --> 00:16:10.553 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I like that idea.

00:16:11.262 --> 00:16:12.305 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Rika!

00:16:12.389 --> 00:16:14.432 position:50% align:center
Don't listen to those people!

00:16:15.558 --> 00:16:16.351 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Ai?

00:16:16.434 --> 00:16:19.104 position:50% align:center
Yep. And not just me.

00:16:19.187 --> 00:16:20.647 position:50% align:center
Everybody's here.

00:16:20.730 --> 00:16:23.149 position:50% align:center
Yeah. This isn't like you, Rika.

00:16:23.233 --> 00:16:24.734 position:50% align:center
Don't give up.

00:16:24.818 --> 00:16:27.237 position:50% align:center
Not in a place like this!

00:16:27.320 --> 00:16:30.031 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
And what, exactly, is "like me"?

00:16:30.949 --> 00:16:31.908 position:50% align:center
Rika!

00:16:31.991 --> 00:16:33.201 position:50% align:center
Pull yourself together!

00:16:33.284 --> 00:16:34.285 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Come on!

00:16:34.369 --> 00:16:35.912 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Please! Just talk to us, Rika!

00:16:35.995 --> 00:16:37.247 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Hang in there!

00:16:37.330 --> 00:16:38.790 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Snap out of it!

00:16:39.958 --> 00:16:42.836 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Man. I'm just so tired.

00:16:42.919 --> 00:16:44.295 position:50% align:center
[CENTIPEDE]
Then relax.

00:16:44.379 --> 00:16:47.465 position:50% align:center
Surrender yourself to me.

00:16:49.843 --> 00:16:51.094 position:50% align:center
[SHINO]
It's okay, Rika.

00:16:51.177 --> 00:16:54.848 position:50% align:center
Now you can be saved,
just as I was saved.

00:16:54.931 --> 00:16:57.225 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Yeah. I'd like that.

00:16:59.102 --> 00:17:01.104 position:50% align:center
Make it go away.

00:17:01.187 --> 00:17:03.773 position:50% align:center
Oh my. Will we lose one?

00:17:03.857 --> 00:17:05.567 position:50% align:center
Seems possible.

00:17:05.650 --> 00:17:10.113 position:50% align:center
Now... I shall give
you the hug of life!

00:17:12.198 --> 00:17:13.616 position:50% align:center
Father.

00:17:23.168 --> 00:17:24.586 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:17:26.338 --> 00:17:27.839 position:50% align:center
Mannen.

00:17:28.423 --> 00:17:30.300 position:50% align:center
What's that turtle doing?

00:17:30.383 --> 00:17:32.093 position:50% align:center
What are you doing?

00:17:32.177 --> 00:17:34.679 position:50% align:center
You're supposed to deal
with the Haters, remember?

00:17:38.558 --> 00:17:39.726 position:50% align:center
That's right.

00:17:39.809 --> 00:17:42.270 position:50% align:center
Mannen imprinted on me.

00:17:42.354 --> 00:17:44.606 position:50% align:center
So he thinks I'm his mom.

00:17:48.651 --> 00:17:52.364 position:50% align:center
You have to keep your mom safe.

00:17:56.159 --> 00:17:57.827 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Rika!

00:17:57.911 --> 00:17:58.745 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Please, Rika!

00:17:58.828 --> 00:17:59.913 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Come back to us!

00:17:59.996 --> 00:18:00.830 position:50% align:center
[AI] We're all here
for you, so please!

00:18:00.914 --> 00:18:02.332 position:50% align:center
Mannen!

00:18:04.959 --> 00:18:06.044 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
That was close.

00:18:06.127 --> 00:18:07.212 position:50% align:center
Another minute and
I would have turned into

00:18:07.295 --> 00:18:10.006 position:50% align:center
a selfish, piece-of-shit mother.

00:18:10.090 --> 00:18:13.259 position:50% align:center
My mom isn't perfect,
but she did teach me one thing.

00:18:13.343 --> 00:18:15.303 position:50% align:center
Men who beg women
for their money...

00:18:16.680 --> 00:18:19.140 position:50% align:center
...are nothing but
a bunch of fakes!

00:18:24.312 --> 00:18:25.689 position:50% align:center
No, that isn't true!

00:18:25.772 --> 00:18:27.941 position:50% align:center
My teacher isn't a fake!

00:18:28.024 --> 00:18:30.985 position:50% align:center
He channels--the whole cosmos!

00:18:31.069 --> 00:18:32.946 position:50% align:center
Believe whatever you want!

00:18:36.074 --> 00:18:41.663 position:50% align:center
[RIKA] Who cares--if he
channels it--or scrambles it?

00:18:42.330 --> 00:18:45.417 position:50% align:center
[RIKA roars]

00:18:51.047 --> 00:18:54.342 position:50% align:center
[RIKA laughs]

00:18:54.426 --> 00:18:56.803 position:50% align:center
Mannen. Let's go!

00:18:58.471 --> 00:19:03.184 position:50% align:center
I'll knock you off your
feet--with a shot to the heart!

00:19:19.576 --> 00:19:22.078 position:50% align:center
Whoa! You're a heavy fella.

00:19:26.166 --> 00:19:28.084 position:50% align:center
There there.

00:19:28.168 --> 00:19:29.127 position:50% align:center
I don't get it.

00:19:29.210 --> 00:19:31.087 position:50% align:center
You're weak, too.

00:19:31.171 --> 00:19:33.465 position:50% align:center
You cut yourself.

00:19:33.548 --> 00:19:35.675 position:50% align:center
You're right.

00:19:35.759 --> 00:19:37.052 position:50% align:center
But that's why I have
to keep coming

00:19:37.135 --> 00:19:38.803 position:50% align:center
to this place and fighting.

00:19:38.887 --> 00:19:41.598 position:50% align:center
So I can balance my priorities.

00:19:41.681 --> 00:19:43.391 position:50% align:center
It's true I'm weak.

00:19:43.475 --> 00:19:46.186 position:50% align:center
But... that's the real me.

00:19:48.438 --> 00:19:50.899 position:50% align:center
I may be hurting myself.

00:19:50.982 --> 00:19:52.734 position:50% align:center
But I'm going to live!

00:19:57.280 --> 00:19:58.656 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Rika!

00:19:58.740 --> 00:20:01.368 position:50% align:center
Whoa, Ai!
This is the real "hug of life."

00:20:06.831 --> 00:20:08.792 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Rika.

00:20:08.875 --> 00:20:11.127 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Rika.

00:20:14.255 --> 00:20:16.007 position:50% align:center
Please don't die.

00:20:19.594 --> 00:20:21.012 position:50% align:center
Same to you.

00:20:22.889 --> 00:20:25.475 position:50% align:center
So then! What's on
the agenda today, girls?

00:20:25.558 --> 00:20:26.559 position:50% align:center
[laughter]

00:20:26.643 --> 00:20:27.977 position:50% align:center
[AI]
You tell us!

00:20:35.402 --> 00:20:37.987 position:50% align:center
You're still awake?

00:20:38.071 --> 00:20:40.532 position:50% align:center
I got hungry.

00:20:40.615 --> 00:20:42.742 position:50% align:center
There's some cake in the fridge.

00:20:44.828 --> 00:20:46.955 position:50% align:center
[CHIAKI]
Probably all dried out, though.

00:20:48.957 --> 00:20:52.335 position:50% align:center
Oh, wow. Life is rough.

00:20:52.419 --> 00:20:55.255 position:50% align:center
When did I get so damn old?

00:20:56.381 --> 00:20:58.174 position:50% align:center
You're only 40.

00:20:59.884 --> 00:21:01.553 position:50% align:center
I'm 38.

00:21:04.931 --> 00:21:06.474 position:50% align:center
You were right.

00:21:06.558 --> 00:21:08.018 position:50% align:center
It is dry.

00:21:08.852 --> 00:21:11.646 position:50% align:center
Sometimes...

00:21:11.730 --> 00:21:14.941 position:50% align:center
...I feel like you'll
abandon me, too, Rika.

00:21:15.025 --> 00:21:17.068 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Mm.

00:21:19.154 --> 00:21:21.614 position:50% align:center
But... not right now.

00:21:25.994 --> 00:21:26.870 position:50% align:center
Oh.

00:22:58.420 --> 00:22:59.879 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
To be continued.